verbose_text: A study by Dupuis et al. in SOD1 G86R mice found aberrations of energy metabolism such as reduction of adiposity, increased energy expenditure and lipolysis, and examined the effects of a high fat diet that consisted of regular chow supplemented with 21% (wt/wt) butter fat and 0.15% (wt/wt) cholesterol.
evidence: SOD1 G86R  mice found aberrations of energy metabolism such as reduction of adiposity, increased energy expenditure
